riences on board.\n\nBeyond his career, Paolo is an avid sailor and enjoys playing soccer with\nfriends and family, as well as cycling in nature—activities that reflect his\n\nenergetic and adventurous spirit. His enthusiasm, empathy, and hands-\non approach make him a valued captain, ensuring every journey\n\naboard THYKE II is both seamless and unforgettable."},{"name":"Giacomo Borruso","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::77931f4f-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::abad45c0-2999-11f0-83ba-8d83eb7f7144/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nLanguages: Italian, English.\n\nWith an extensive career at sea, Giacomo Borruso is a highly skilled and passionate seafarer. A dedicated sailor, he has competed in numerous sailing championships, refining his expertise and deepening his connection to the ocean.\n\nBeyond yachting, Giacomo is also a Personal Trainer, dedicating his winters to sports and fitness. His active lifestyle reflects his energetic and disciplined nature, which translates into his work on board. A true outdoorsman, he has a great love for animals and enjoys fishing in his free time.\n\nWith his strong work ethic, technical skills, and enthusiasm for life at sea, Giacomo is a valuable asset to the THYKE II crew, always ensuring a seamless and enjoyable experience for guests."},{"name":"Vitalba Cacioppo","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::77931f4f-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::3feb8f30-299a-11f0-8808-4f51749b8df4/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nLanguages: Italian, English.\n\nPassionate, talented, and deeply rooted in Mediterranean culinary traditions, Vitalba Cacioppo brings an authentic taste of Sicily to THYKE II. Specializing in both savory and sweet Sicilian cuisine, she masterfully combines fresh, local ingredients with time-honored recipes to create unforgettable dining experiences on board.\n\nBeyond her culinary skills, Vitalba is known for her warm and professional demeanor. Her ability to connect with guests ensures a welcoming and refined atmosphere, making every moment on board feel special. Dedicated to excellence, she seamlessly blends hospitality with her love for cooking, adding a personal touch to each charter.\n\nWith her expertise, passion, and engaging personality, Vitalba is an invaluable asset to the THYKE II crew, elevating every journey with exceptional flavors and heartfelt hospitality."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":3800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":4600000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":4600000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"July & August","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":4600000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":4600000,"amount":4600000,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.22}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.35,"unitPrice":4600000,"amount":1610000}],"total":7222000,"subTotal":6210000,"totalTax":1012000},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Sardinia","type":"Geo subunit","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Sardinia"],"coordinates":[8.96574354539669,40.12242872762209],"bbox":[8.180859375000011,38.90966796875,9.805273437500006,41.257080078125]},{"label":"Italy","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Italy"],"coordinates":[12.204840429521369,41.61169587639921],"bbox":[6.6027283120000675,35.48924388200004,18.517425977000073,47.08521494500006]},{"label":"Corsica","type":"Geo subunit","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Corsica"],"coordinates":[9.104917129771797,42.161865413836736],"bbox":[8.565625000000011,41.384912109374994,9.556445312500